    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo septuagesimo quinto, octavo kalende octubris,
                        indictione nona. Manifesti sumus nos <persName>Mothiconis</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Bernardi</persName> et <persName>Gualgerius</persName> et
                            <persName>Iacobus</persName> germani filii suprascripti Mothiconis et
                            <persName>Floredepero</persName> uxor suprascripti Gualgerii, (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia <persName>Belloni</persName> et
                            <persName>Alfani</persName> germanorum meorum (…) insimul per hanc
                        cartulam vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Montanus"
                                >Montanino</name></persName>, rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Hospitals">Altopasso</placeName></orgName> (…), videlicet
                        petiam unam de terra nostra que est in loco ubi dicitur Ad Arbium, que est
                        cultra una, que tenet unum caput in terra <persName>Tiniosi</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Cechi</persName>, alterum in terra heredis quondam
                            <persName>Grungi</persName>, latus unum tenet in <rs key="#Forests"
                            >bosco</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3229" key="#Forests">Silva
                            Salese</placeName>, alterum *** (…). <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: lib.
                        decem bonorum denariorum. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et
                        insuper penam argenti optimi lib. VI. (…) Actum in <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castro</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3211" key="#Castle"
                            >Vivinaria</placeName> prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Michaelis</orgName>. (…) <persName
                            key="#Witness">Guilicio</persName> quondam <persName>Lamberti</persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness">Baialardus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Aldobrandini</persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Rodolfinus</persName> quondam <persName>Bernardi</persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary">Aldricus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> donni imperatoris post traditam complevi et
                        dedi. (…)</ab>
